	<description><![CDATA[<p>Hi Nic. A slightly trivial question, what's your advice on choosing an appropriate essay title? </p>
<p>Im not sure how general/specific to be. I understand this must direct the reader but I dont want to narrow my options when writing. For example, with your practice question I was thinking something like;</p>
<p>'Does faith distort perceptions and change the reality?'</p>
<p>Thanks.</p>
